@startuml 效果评测与复盘分析时序图

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam participantFontSize 13
skinparam noteFontSize 11

actor 用户 as User
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "TaskController" as TC
participant "ProcessScheduler" as PS
participant "MetricCalculator" as MC
participant "ReportGenerator" as RGen
participant "ReplayManager" as RM

User -> Frontend : 创建验证任务并配置场景
Frontend -> TC : create_task(scenario, config)
TC --> Frontend : 返回 task_id
User -> Frontend : 启动任务
Frontend -> TC : start_task(task_id)
TC -> PS : schedule(task_id)
PS -> PS : 依次执行环境初始化、攻击、防御、态势分析
PS --> TC : 返回流程执行完成
TC --> Frontend : 返回任务完成状态
Frontend --> User : 展示任务完成及各阶段状态

User -> Frontend : 点击生成报告
Frontend -> MC : calculate_all(task_id)
MC -> MC : 计算攻击、防御、资源各项指标
MC -> RGen : generate_report(task_id, metrics)
RGen --> MC : 返回 Report
MC --> Frontend : 返回指标汇总与报告
Frontend --> User : 展示评估报告

User -> Frontend : 点击回放
Frontend -> RM : build_timeline(task_id)
RM -> RM : 构建回放时间轴
RM --> Frontend : 返回回放数据
Frontend --> User : 展示过程回放时间轴

@enduml
